description:
Pine-Sol® Multi-Surface Cleaner, Original, helps you keep your entire house clean with a Classic Pine scent. This multi surface cleaner cuts through the toughest stains, grease and grime. Use Pine-Sol® Multi-Surface Cleaner to keep your entire home, from the kitchen to the bathroom to the garage, sparkling and smelling clean. That's the power of Pine-Sol®.

Usage Directions: General Cleaning: Use ¼ cup per gallon of water. No rinse required except on rubber or asphalt tile. On tough jobs, use full strength. Rinse immediately. For no-wax floors, only use diluted and rinse. Do not use on marble, aluminum, or wood that is unfinished, unsealed, unpainted, waxed, oiled, worn. Toilet Bowls: Pour ½ cup in the bowl. Brush thoroughly. Laundry: Rub in full-strength on heavily soiled areas pre-wash. For extra cleaning, add ½ cup to load. Use on white or colorfast fabrics.

Caution Statements: EYE IRRITANT. Do not get in eyes. For sensitive skin or prolonged use, wear rubber gloves. FIRST AID: EYES – Immediately rinse with water for 15 minutes. If irritation persists, call a doctor. IF SWALLOWED – Drink a glassful of water. Call a doctor or a poison control center. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. CONTAINS: Alkyl alcohol ethoxylates. CONTAINER DISPOSAL: Offer empty container for recycling. If recycling is not available, discard container in trash.

description:
Reveal your wood floor's natural beauty. Bringing out the natural beauty of your wood floors can be as simple as a quick cleaning. Pledge® Gentle Wood Floor Cleaner is a ready-to-use specially designed to safely and gently remove dirt and grime that built up over time from hardwood floors* without leaving behind a dull, sticky residue. Just squirt and mop it to enjoy a natural shine and that classic Pledge® lemon scent any time you like. Enough with the scuff, give yourself floors you can be proud of. *Safe to use only on finished, sealed surfaces.

DIRECTIONS FOR USE: Use Pledge Floor Care Wood Squirt & Mop directly from the bottle. No mixing or diluting is required. 1. Squirt directly onto floor in a 3' by 3' area using an "S" pattern. 2. Using a well-wrung mop, clean squirted area thoroughly. NOTE: Not recommended for use on unfinished, unsealed, waxed, oiled, or worn flooring. Do not allow puddles of cleaner to remain on floor. Test in an inconspicuous area prior to use.

USES: GREAT FOR: Wood floors such as sealed wood and laminate wood flooring. NOT RECOMMENDED FOR: Furniture or unfinished, waxed, oiled, or worn wood floors.

INGREDIENTS: Water, ethoxylated alcohol, methylisothiazolinone, trideceth-3, fragrance, and potassium hydroxide. SCJ Formula #35*3590
title: Pledge FloorCare Wood Squirt & Mop 27oz

bullets: Ready to use
Quickly cleans wood floors
Streak-free, residue-free
Reveal your wood floor's natural beauty
Lemon scent

description: Pine-Sol Multi-Surface Cleaner, Original, helps you keep your entire house clean with a Classic Pine scent. This multi surface cleaner cuts through the toughest stains, grease and grime. Use Pine-Sol Multi-Surface Cleaner to keep your entire home, from the kitchen to the bathroom to the garage, sparkling and smelling clean. That's the power of Pine-Sol. Usage Directions: General Cleaning: Use cup per gallon of water. No rinse required except on rubber or asphalt tile. On tough jobs, use full strength. Rinse immediately. For no-wax floors, only use diluted and rinse. Do not use on marble, aluminum, or wood that is unfinished, unsealed, unpainted, waxed, oiled, worn. Toilet Bowls: Pour cup in the bowl. Brush thoroughly. Laundry: Rub in full-strength on heavily soiled areas pre-wash. For extra cleaning, add cup to load. Use on white or colorfast fabrics.Ingredients: Alkyl alcohol ethoxylates. CONTAINS BIODEGRADABLE CLEANING AGENTS, CONTAINS NO PHOSPHORUS.Warnings: EYE IRRITANT. Do not get in eyes. For sensitive skin or prolonged use, wear rubber gloves. FIRST AID: EYES Immediately rinse with water for 15 minutes. If irritation persists, call a doctor. IF SWALLOWED Drink a glassful of water. Call a doctor or a poison control center. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. CONTAINS: Alkyl alcohol ethoxylates. CONTAINER DISPOSAL: Offer empty container for recycling. If recycling is not available, discard container in trash.
title: Pine-Sol Multi-Surface Cleaner Original 100 oz
